But he's probably bluffing!
I'll show him something important instead!

32
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:21,277
Incredible!
I can hear the engine singing.

33
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:33,156
It's music beats in unison
with the beating of my heart!

34
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,550
Now me and the
machine are one.

35
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:40,758
Come on, sing!
Sing louder!

36
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:06,676
He's pulling me.

37
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:31,109
- What?
- Fantastic!

38
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:34,078
That car has an engine much
more powerful than a Formula 3!

39
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:36,037
H-Hiziri...!

40
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:41,231
How did he do that?
I'm pushing my car to the limit!

41
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:43,356
Is it possible
for me to go faster?

42
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:47,917
It will be an
impossible task for his car.

43
