His potential is
higher than yours!

44
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,957
I warn you that
Hiziri is in great shape!

45
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,076
And he is absolutely
determined to win!

46
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:57,478
And he must do it!
Otherwise next year,

47
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,437
he won't be able
to race in Formula 1!

48
