He won't be able to race in Formula 1!
He won't be able to race in Formula 1!

49
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:10,700
So...
Hiziri isn't bluffing after all,

50
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,996
He asked me to follow him so he could...

51
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:15,036
... laugh at my inferiority!

52
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:28,675
Finally the world is in my hands!

53
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,755
I don't think
Hiziri saw the signal.

54
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:54,435
I-I've never seen anything like it!

55
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,397
After many laps of high speed his

56
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,357
engine shows no signs of slowing down!

57
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:00,829
This is all because of Tamotsu's abilities.

58
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,876
Isn't that right, Eijiro?

59
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,477
Here comes sempai.

60
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:12,668
My car can't
go faster than that!

61
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:16,192
Gunma is really
giving it his all.

62
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,436
But he can't overcome Hiziri!

63
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:21,757
- Unless a miracle happens ...
- A miracle ?!

64
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:24,709
Hiziri is going strong,

65
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:27,678
However, his engine could stop working.

66
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:33,717
This is it! I've had enough
of being behind Hiziri ...

67
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:36,234
...and eating his dust!
At the cost of ...

68
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:39,278
...breaking the engine,
I will surpass him!

69
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:44,268
Hiziri is above his own limits!

70
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:47,876
And he's definitely not afraid.

71
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:50,076
And that means only one thing:

72
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:53,915
Hiziri is by far the
greatest driver of all time!

73
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:05,028
It's a miracle!
I've never felt so warm inside!

74
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:08,277
And this means that
the fatal moment is near!

75
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:12,434
The degradation of the
suspension, tires and brakes,

76
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:15,757
the roar of the engine, the valves,
the movement of the pistons ...

77
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,836
I can feel it in my hands.

78
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:21,551
Every square inch of asphalt
and every little wildfire,

79
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:24,950
has the lust of a diamond!

80
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:32,036
The grass, the trees, the flowers ...

81
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:35,278
Right now their colors seem
more beautiful than ever.

82
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:38,519
I've never noticed,
how beautiful nature is.

83
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,674
Unfortunately, I've
realized it too late.

84
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,596
This world is full of light!

85
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:56,155
I've never seen
so much in my life!

86
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:59,436
Are you following me , Gunma?

87
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:03,633
It's wonderful! I feel like
I'm in control of his life!

88
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:09,469
I wonder why he
didn't see the signal.

89
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,559
Tamotsu...

90
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,797
He's hurt!

91
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:28,036
Thanks for everything, Tamostu!

92
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:31,630
This machine was the
best gift I've ever received!

93
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:35,076
Glory awaits!

94
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,351
But instead of me,

95
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:40,151
share it with your friend Gunma.

96
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:58,156
I'm so sorry!

97
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,515
But ... I can't!

98
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:05,148
I promised not
to stop your race.

99
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,236
You decide your own fate.

100
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,476
Now it's just you and me, Hiziri!

101
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:17,558
Ever since this race began
I've done nothing but hang back.

102
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:21,073
But I am the
fastest on the track!

103
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:23,037
And I'll prove it.

104
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,230
I have to hurry,
we're on the final lap!

105
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:30,636
The track is perfect and
I'm not even forcing the engine!

106
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:35,270
But if I put myself in his wake,
I should be able to overcome him!

107
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:39,039
Yes!
This is it!

108
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:47,753
Yes! Just when
he least expects it!

109
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:51,036
I ask only one thing, Gunma!

110
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:56,679
I'll teach you how a great
champion behaves on the track!

111
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,357
H-Hiziri.

112
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:08,678
Is that so, Hiziri!

113
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:11,189
Now I know what you
were going to teach me!

114
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:30,836
Hey! Slow down!

115
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:33,480
If you continue like this,
the engine is likely to melt.

116
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:35,471
Let's try that again.

117
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:37,949
Speed up and drag
me like you did before.

118
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:41,677
And when you do,
I won't hesitate to overtake you!

119
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,711
Gunma! Slow down!

120
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:47,075
You can't continue at that speed!

121
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:49,471
Come on, Hiziri! Why the wait?

122
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:51,556
Do that trick you did again!

123
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:55,436
This time I'll show you that
I have learned this lesson well!

124
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:02,810
Gunma Akagi?
So he's still with me, that's good.

125
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,517
Great! He's accelerating!

126
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:17,950
If I can take full advantage
of his trail, I'll pass him easily!

127
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,756
I only hope that the
motor keeps working.

128
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:56,557
Ah!

129
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:08,077
Huh...

130
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:13,500
Hiziri?

131
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,756
What's going on?

132
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,436
Why isn't Hiziri following me?

133
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:47,111
He can't have gave up so easily!

134
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:51,192
Hiziri better be alright!
Hiziri better be alright!

135
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:15,278
