- How did this happen?

137
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,675
I don't know!
Maybe it was the brakes!

138
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:23,356
Hiziri!

139
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,355
Hiziri, what's wrong with you?

140
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,630
