144
00:14:03,800 --> 00:14:05,677
Good luck!

145
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:15,957
Hiziri!

146
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:37,110
Wait!
I will take off his helmet.

147
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:48,036
And his mask!

148
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:51,836
Your free now,
you can breath.

149
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:03,428
Look at you...
We have to do something...

150
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:06,036
or your skills will suffer.

151
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,957
Where are you taking him?

152
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:46,596
I'll teach you how a great
champion behaves on the track!

153
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:49,599
All you gotta do is
keep up with me, Gunma.

154
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:52,553
Thank you Hiziri, for this lesson.

155
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:56,679
You are a great driver and I
will try to follow your example.

156
00:15:57,200 --> 00:16:00,351
Hiziri asked me to
become his mechanic!

157
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:03,918
I can't explain the reason why,

158
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:07,072
but I can't betray the
promise that I made to Hiziri.

159
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:10,148
- Please forgive me!
- Forgive you!

160
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:12,236
Only now I
understand why you did it!

161
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:18,750
Gunma!

162
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:21,750
Hiziri!

163
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,671
Tamostu!
The champagne!

164
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:23,313
You are the winner!
Forgive me for being presumptuous.

165
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:37,672
Goodbye, Hiziri
... my friend!

166
00:18:04,320 --> 00:18:07,517
What a bunch of idiots!
Risking their lives on the track

167
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:09,670
...and now look at what's happened.

168
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,956
Come on, let's go!

169
